      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of life left? This car is in honest, fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some expected wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid and reliable choice for anyone seeking value and functionality. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a quality vehicle at a budget-friendly price!",
